verbose_text: The molecular analysis evaluates the incidence of molecular variants, using sets of specific primers for SS18-SSX1 and SS18-SSX2; however, a statistically significant association between histological subtype (monophasic vs. biphasic) and SSX1 or SSX2 has not been found.
evidence: association between histological subtype (monophasic vs. biphasic) and SSX1 or SSX2
